nception  as I abhor the damage done by large numbers of pleasure  vehicles roaring along unmetalled tracks/roads and the disturbance such activity does to the peace of the wonderful countryside, as well as the health and safety issues posed to walkers, cyclists and those on horseback and the inconvenience to farmers.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">I live on a farm within the boundaries of the Norfolk Broads and also spend time walking in the Yorkshire Dales and Northumberland National Parks.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Please add my name in support of the two proposals/petitions. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">These proposals/petitions also supported by Kurt Angelrath, Member Yorkshire Dales Green Lanes Alliance</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">September 2013</span></p><div style="width:auto; height:21.85pt; float:left;"><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="RAMFooter2"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">2</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> of </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">1</span></a></p></div><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>